Resource Profile: openIMIS Insurance Plan

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-insurance-plan Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISInsurancePlan

Defines an Insurance Plan for openIMIS which maps to a Product.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Conversion Product (InsurancePlan) and openIMIS Contract
  • Examples for this Profile: Regional fixed enrolment and Regional fixed enrolment
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
